&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;# Heading 1
## Heading 2
### Heading 3
#### Heading 4
##### Heading 5
###### Heading 6&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
